Package ibis.frontend

Interface Summary
ByteCodeWrapper This interface serves as a wrapper interface for different bytecode rewriters.
ClassInfo This interface is a wrapper for different bytecode rewriters, encapsulating methods that apply to a specific class.
 

Class Summary
BCELClassInfo BCEL implementation of the ClassInfo interface.
BCELWrapper BCEL implementation of the ByteCodeWrapper interface.
Ibisc The main class of the Ibisc frontend.
IbiscComponent This abstract class must be implemented by all components that are to be part of the Ibis frontend framework, and is the only means through which the Ibis frontend framework communicates with the component.
JarEntryInfo Maintains information about the content of a jarfile entry.
JarInfo Maintains information about the contents of a jarfile.
